  greater is required for Windows 98 ,XP, ME, and 2k.</EM> </P>  <P><STRONG>1.10.1 Can EverQuest run on NT or
  Windows 2000? </STRONG><A></A><STRONG><BR></STRONG>EverQuest <EM>should</EM> run under Windows 2000, however there are still
  problems with some 3D cards, their drivers, and Windows 2000. EverQuest will
