  used?</STRONG><A></A><STRONG><BR></STRONG>EverQuest requires DirectX&nbsp;8.1 or newer.</P>  <P>&nbsp;</P>  <P><STRONG>1.11.4 Does EverQuest support OpenGL? </STRONG><A></A><STRONG><BR></STRONG>EverQuest uses Glide (the native 3dfx API) and Direct 3D (Microsoft API
  that most modern 3d cards support). We do not support OpenGL (nothing against
  it, just with both Glide and D3D, there's no real need).</P>  <P>&nbsp;</P>  <P><STRONG>1.12 Is the game downloadable or is it
  on CD?</STRONG><A></A><STRONG><BR></STRONG>CD-ROM.</P>  <P>&nbsp;</P>  <P><STRONG>1.13 What kind of music is there in
